Show HN: Test-driven development spreadsheet to track ChatGPT's failures
text:
The recent discussion on "test-driven development"[1] made me want to track some of the most obvious failings I observe in ChatGPT.

Here is my publicly viewable spreadsheet:

https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vRwijLG35NlPdee3Gj_VBAgvYoYjyfz6eQIlWsujH6-v623eHzH_qqstYKd304599tQAkGBEzkhr7Vm/pubhtml

You can add to it by completing the questions (just two are required, the prompt it got wrong and its wrong answer):

https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeUi8ewl8Y8upHMUntswnQ2hxtgm-UojVFwajE6gHXER5d9Mw/viewform?usp=sf_link

Feel free to list any other failures you've observed!

[1] https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=34467523
